<HEAD>Teen Heartthrob Debbie Gibson Graduates from High School</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MERRICK, N.Y. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Pop singer Debbie Gibson traded her show
business attire for a cap and gown, blending in with 300 other
graduates at Calhoun High School.
