<HEAD>A Statistical Look At Atlanta</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ATLANTA (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are some facts and figures about Atlanta,
home of the 1988 Democratic National Convention. Statistics are for
the metro area unless otherwise noted.
