compared with 74.1 percent a year earlier.
   Net tonnage by district for the week ended June 25: Northeast
Coast, 273,000; Pittsburgh, 194,000; Youngstown, 93,000; Lake Erie,
139,000; Detroit, 158,000; Chicago, 486,000; Midwest, 176,000;
Southern, 206,000; and Western, 94,000.
